<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Server Offline</title>
<style>
body{
margin:0;
height:100vh;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
background:#0a0a0f;
color:#ffffff;
font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
text-align:center;
}
.box{
padding:40px;
background:#111118;
border-radius:14px;
border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
box-shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
}
h1{
font-size:42px;
letter-spacing:2px;
color:#e63946;
margin-bottom:10px;
}
p{
font-size:16px;
color:#cccccc;
}
.dot{
width:10px;
height:10px;
background:#e63946;
border-radius:50%;
display:inline-block;
margin-right:8px;
animation:pulse 1.2s infinite;
}
@keyframes pulse{
0%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}
50%{opacity:.4;transform:scale(.7)}
100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="box">
<h1><span class="dot"></span>SERVER OFFLINE</h1>
<p>Due to inconsistency of network.</p>
<p>Please check again later.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
